SHORELINE
EQUITY PARTNERS
September 20, 2023
Solamere Capital AF III, L.P.
Shoreline Equity Partners Fund, L.P.
RE: Net Capital Call due October 4, 2023
Dear Partner:
In accordance with Shoreline Equity Partners Fund, L.P.'s Amended and Restated Agreement of Limited
Partnership ("Partnership Agreement"), we are calling capital of $4.5 million (net of a Mr. Greens escrow
distribution). Capitalized terms used but not defined herein shall have the meanings ascribed to such terms in the
Partnership Agreement.
Shoreline invested an additional $5.1 million in C&S Chemicals in April of this year. The funds were utilized to
complete an add-on acquisition, Southwest Engineers. The investment was comprised of $5.1 million in preferred
and common equity. At the close of these transactions, Shoreline currently has invested capital of $35.0 million
in C&S Chemicals.
The remaining $1.1 million is being utilized to repay line of credit draws for partnership expenses.
On or before October 4, 2023, please wire $124,392.48, representing your portion of this net capital call to:
